snippet.title: Disney & LAPD Hauled Into Johnny Depp’s $50M Defamation Suit Against Amber Heard #disney #johnnydepp
snippet.description:

Johnny Depp may believe he has handed Amber Heard all the documentation he is required to in the former couple’s multimillion-dollar defamation battles, but the Aquaman star is now going fishing in some very deep seas. In subpoenas submitted today, Heard wants to know what the Los Angeles Police department and Walt Disney Motion Picture Group have on the ex-Pirates of the Caribbean actor. It is information that she and her Virginia attorney want produced in the coming weeks.
